export const images = {
  logoHeaderWhite: require('static/Assets/Image/Icon/logoHeaderWhite.svg'),
  logoHeaderBlack: require('static/Assets/Image/Icon/logoHeaderBlack.svg'),
  giveawayTextWhite: require('static/Assets/Image/Icon/giveawayTextWhite.svg'),
  giveawayTextBlack: require('static/Assets/Image/Icon/giveawayTextBlack.svg'),
  aLogoBlack: require('static/Assets/Image/Icon/ALogoBlack.svg'),
  aLogoWhite: require('static/Assets/Image/Icon/ALogoWhite.svg'),
  instagramIcon: require('static/Assets/Image/Icon/instagramIcon.svg'),
  facebookIcon: require('static/Assets/Image/Icon/facebookIcon.svg'),
  consignmentForm: require('static/Assets/Image/Lottie/consignmentForm.json'),
  successJson: require('static/Assets/Image/Lottie/success.json'),
  rightArrowJson: require('static/Assets/Image/Lottie/rightArrow.json'),
  founderAvatar: require('static/Assets/Image/founder-avater.jpeg'),

  favicon: require('static/favicon.png'),
  threeDots: require('static/Assets/Image/Common/three-dots.svg'),
  error: require('static/Assets/Image/Common/error.png'),
  pageNotFound: require('static/Assets/Image/Common/404.svg'),
  flags: {
    'en': require('static/Assets/Image/Flags/en.png'),
    'ja': require('static/Assets/Image/Flags/ja.png'),
    'cn': require('static/Assets/Image/Flags/cn.png')
  }
}
